translation[6]{c,v,t}:
  53,45,"Ɔno na Ɔbͻͻ adeε mmienu mmienu, ͻbarima ne ͻbaa-,"
  53,46,"Fri ahobaeε mu wͻ εberε a εbεpue aba."
  53,47,"Ɔno na Daakye Wusͻreε no (ho asεm) da Ne soͻ."
  53,48,"Ɔno na Ɔma ahonya εna Ɔma ohia."
  53,49,"Ɔne (nsoromma Shi’ira) Kyεkyε (a Arabfoͻ abosomsomfoͻ no som no no) Wura."
  53,50,"Ɔno na Ɔsεee Aad, tetefoͻ no,"
  53,51,"Samuudfoͻ no nso Wamma wͻn mu biara anka."
  53,52,"Ɛna Noa nkorͻfoͻ no a wͻdii (Aadfoͻ ne Samuudfoͻ no) anim kan no, na wͻyε nnebͻneεfoͻ, atuatefoͻ."
  53,53,"Ne nkuro a abͻ no (Sodom ne Gomora), Ɔno ara na Ɔsεee no."
  53,54,"Deε eyiri faa wͻn no yiri faa wͻn."
  53,55,"Enti (ͻdasani), wo Wura Nyankopͻn adom no mu deε εwͻ hen na w’adwen nsi wo pi wͻ ho?"
  53,56,"(Nkͻmhyεni) woi yε kͻkͻbͻni tesε tetefoͻ no kͻkͻbͻfoͻ no ara pεpεεpε."
  53,57,"Ɛberε no bεn ara na (eguso) rebεn."
  53,58,"Obiara nni hͻ a ɔbɛtumi afrii Nyankopͻn akyi asi ho kwan."
  53,59,"Enti saa asεm woi na εyε mo nwanwa?"
  53,60,"Ɛna moresereε, εna monnsuu,"
  53,61,"Ɛna mode agorͻ resεe mo berε kwa, εna monnwene ho?"
  53,62,"Enti monfa mo anim mutu fͻm ma Nyankopͻn na monsom (no)."
  54,1,IYure sele ifikile yaye nenyanga sele icandeke (kubini)
  54,2,"Ke kaloku xa bebona umqondiso (ummangaliso), bayatshikila bathi: “(Lo) ngumlingo ogqithayo.”"
  54,3,"Kananjalo baye baphika, balandela iminqweno yabo. Kodwa into nganye inexesha lokufezekiswa (kwayo)"
  54,4,Ke kaloku sele ifikile kubo inkcazelo ekukho kuyo isilumkiso (esaneleyo ngokubhekiselele kugabadelo)
  54,5,Ubulumko obuphangaleleyo kodwa isilumkiso asibancedi (nto)
  54,6,"Bayeke ke (Muhammad), ngeMini uMkhwazi aya kubizela abantu kwinto engathandekiyo (uMlilo wesiHogo)"
